"},{"id":"48903897-8a59-43b1-a2fd-48001a59b481","name":"workflow","value":"={{ $workflow.name }}","type":"string"}]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.set","typeVersion":3.4,"position":[3294,1420],"id":"5909d74a-5110-43b8-a1c8-f37ea1464e19","name":"Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"select":"channel","channelId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"#hr","cachedResultName":"#hr"},"text":"=🚨 {{ $json.workflow }} failed at {{ $json.failedNode }}: {{ $json.errorMessage }}","otherOptions":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.slack","typeVersion":2.3,"position":[3618,1420],"id":"804f7103-834e-435e-b716-bbd7cf452e98","name":"Escalate Failure to Slack","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"content":"### New Candidate Form Submission\n\nServes an n8n-hosted form (Email, Role, Stage). Each submission becomes one execution.\n\nNext: Stamp & Shape Candidate","width":280,"height":232,"color":5},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-330,520],"id":"63ff90d6-1551-fbce-542c-6f346d23143b","name":"Note: New Candidate Form Submission"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp & Shape Candidate\n\nShapes the item: writes `candidateId`, `receivedAt`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Payload Valid?","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,520],"id":"00ea2398-61bc-394a-58aa-cf237ccbb823","name":"Note: Stamp & Shape Candidate"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Payload Valid?\n\nTwo-way gate on `={{ $json.candidateId }}`. TRUE continues the happy path, FALSE takes the alternate branch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Route by Work Type · ②→ Record Rejected Input","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"b099da9a-5f23-6dba-8753-9f9c4fcb1965","name":"Note: Payload Valid?"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Record Rejected Input\n\nairtable — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Airtable PAT","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,1030],"id":"3031f27c-130a-cf62-1768-ff36d4d2ae2c","name":"Note: Record Rejected Input"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Route by Work Type\n\nRoutes each item to one of 3 lanes: auto-approve, needs-review + fallback.\n\nPorts: ①→ Process 'auto-approve' → Airtable · ②→ Fast-Track 'needs-review' + Alert · ③→ Hold Unknown Types (DLQ)","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,520],"id":"7bdc0846-9eb5-a810-925a-f37fc20320f2","name":"Note: Route by Work Type"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Process 'auto-approve' → Airtable\n\nairtable — `upsert` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Merge Routed Work · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Airtable PAT","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,250],"id":"f7094811-8c41-e281-75b5-13aab5c565ff","name":"Note: Process 'auto-approve' → Airtable"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fast-Track 'needs-review' + Alert\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Merge Routed Work · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1290,760],"id":"d3b8c28a-214a-a512-4f60-1618f17ec296","name":"Note: Fast-Track 'needs-review' + Alert"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Hold Unknown Types (DLQ)\n\nairtable — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Merge Routed Work · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Airtable PAT","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1614,1270],"id":"15e6b3ea-cfb4-ee1b-abe8-2f8f96ea6a0b","name":"Note: Hold Unknown Types (DLQ)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Merge Routed Work\n\nRejoins 3 branches into one stream (mode: append) so downstream logic runs once.\n\nNext: Sort Candidates Newest First","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2262,520],"id":"52c45c5b-c555-f2b5-af4a-a0be87d2404f","name":"Note: Merge Routed Work"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Sort Candidates Newest First\n\nOrders items (newest first) so limits and digests pick the most relevant records.\n\nNext: Save Execution Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3234,520],"id":"02aadc71-5fc6-8783-5f57-8d02d8da4ffd","name":"Note: Sort Candidates Newest First"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Save Execution Metadata\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Send Summary to Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3558,520],"id":"d0072807-499b-c3ac-eff8-02b9c9a75216","name":"Note: Save Execution Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3882,520],"id":"1a239c10-72b8-0448-95a0-618f7949a7ee","name":"Note: Send Summary to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3234,1540],"id":"7ea2cd10-05c1-ed69-6048-90b707900193","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3558,1540],"id":"3bf17875-ebda-614c-b6f8-1dbba0b4f3d7","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Route documents with Twilio and Airtable end to end\n\n**Pattern:** Approval Workflow · **Level:** Core · **Trigger:** Form\n\n## What it does\nRoute documents with Twilio and Airtable end to end. It starts from a hosted form submission.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual onboarding is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nNew Candidate Form Submission → Stamp & Shape Candidate → Payload Valid? → Route by Work Type → Process 'auto-approve' → Airtable → Merge Routed Work → Sort Candidates Newest First → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to approval workflow without manual effort\n- Anyone automating onboarding in human resources\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Has retries and error handling built in\n- Responds in seconds\n- Saves hours of manual work each week\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: Airtable PAT; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"9045e6fa-67e9-dafc-994b-b8df97a6e3c6","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-290],"id":"1a936a3c-19fb-abaf-bc80-0b9d77cfc170","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your onboarding process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-290],"id":"821c5f4c-a37f-36b8-ea88-bc3989d40940","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"New Candidate Form Submission":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp & Shape Candidate","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp & Shape Candidate":{"main":[[{"node":"Payload Valid?","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Payload Valid?":{"main":[[{"node":"Route by Work Type","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Record Rejected Input","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Route by Work Type":{"main":[[{"node":"Process 'auto-approve' → Airtable","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Fast-Track 'needs-review' + Alert","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Hold Unknown Types (DLQ)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Process 'auto-approve' → Airtable":{"main":[[{"node":"Merge Routed Work","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Fast-Track 'needs-review' + Alert":{"main":[[{"node":"Merge Routed Work","type":"main","index":1}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Hold Unknown Types (DLQ)":{"main":[[{"node":"Merge Routed Work","type":"main","index":2}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Merge Routed Work":{"main":[[{"node":"Sort Candidates Newest First","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Sort Candidates Newest First":{"main":[[{"node":"Save Execution Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Save Execution Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Slack","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Slack","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Slack":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"3f6aaca5-e2b2-4016-b03d-a05021e02ef3","id":"FDX10369"}